LHGKE2_4uzKs5lMvhEgqGA1EK0qS1xlKwnl_ko5YGih6zJvlenmnMRmLSHogUX9vsRbaPCxIrO2iebRQmm-wlKJxVPEUVrFqzhOy-OKfDBVvToPthZsgYgNzA00LXxpkcTZFulaT3Yv3upraNrFdDImUidLbrbaegY3hB_eoEI1FgkUElAJfsU0hA6xCmFuSmpip_HCqNMDxM_ercMUk9Ovl39ekeZk9WHKyANqu1puZtWa02tXxRmoQlSy-8lfzACy6AwQGUQ-L5VUU05chR3VLywFnLcia8668OL23Pfpb5SOCjO4VBHnPb8-4cs7bocZhbzmQnODkjWx07bKhKJsp5xY9wvtynssLeuR9LiQePZIyK5wCOzc2_uFg5a2YFNP1yXyWhY6T-CZ9hpW7TooVdMjofgK_XHow2cKuhkOnxCLfSQTteFmtNbX8MxB3xAG4t5YcCEF81T3UsvJUPXsDx8jU8P6Zit69BUd7chpPzYdcuBDJUA_FRum00mBRNnltud4VnfdQGqXnMYOSnTrp8VFbmW0uzT63dYbLze6ZiZkOnB1vNxyag4muWzKXzcuTNex8MhCM9yF0-D2HGv12ZNqjI-qAKPy7VHQfUo6apBgVOy3TJKDPxzQ1W1EMNFvGgC09fLwYhHDq4-eOoPfhNHosQifEZs99PIjTXnmbGZGxo9MLR3m3XozDUnkftl42neISdhqxVlNZFL2aN_SOubIo1SqZvc-QUXkK_roqLjdnjptdJE3jDaNccLm55PfVA9RDOKJ6ekgmhLb1KrL-Rn0QLTcd34iOb4WURhHh6AxucphrFfMB2yztiniU37_ndHOXg2Oy9PRPxMYmnT09NeDjFSHHoh-hCv-JP7TQhnlfBe6taiA4oWlREpiDveGnaM_vcyltz80H4LODt-jYPFZbVC9_Tzjb8Ulss0mO8_xdtIVinzL07pE3b3rqptTQrAPyytSV2LY9QqXz7m38Qcpc5z6Tm33kUZcT_jy8HavfEjcVwZhnGz786k8g_yukNOxdVlUWyLREhGSu3tg2M=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating native image runtime checks**\\n\\nI'm thinking that we shouldn't use isNativeImageRuntime guards and instead just remove the runtime checks. I wonder about catching errors only. If the native test passes—even with extra catches—it might be okay? But we definitely don't want to broaden anything unnecessarily. The key question is that to pass the native test, none of these tests should fail. In the native image, there’s a concern about ClassLoader potentially causing ClassNotFound issues with URLClassLoader.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering JDK details**\\n\\nI’m looking into JDK 25, and it seems the jrt file system is still required. However, property 11 indicating isAtLeastJava9 is a positive sign. I should use versions 17.0.1 or 21.0.1. But then, for the older IntelliJ, maybe I should parse the JavaVersion as 17? I’m curious if that will work well with the setup. It seems like I’m figuring out compatibility and setup issues here.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_joB8oi6hB57iHp9l9C3nkoNr|fc_030a149c44bfa1620169f9fb91af4881a084c5f4a843e7ccb5", "name": "edit", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/com.diffplug.spotless/spotless-lib/2.45.0/src/test/java/com_diffplug_spotless/spotless_lib/KtfmtStepInnerStateTest.java", "edits": [{"oldText": "    private static String formatWithRuntimeClassLoadingSupport(FormatterStep step) throws Exception {\n        try {\n            return step.format(KOTLIN_SOURCE, Formatter.NO_FILE_SENTINEL);\n        } catch (IllegalArgumentException exception) {\n            if (!isOldKtfmtJavaVersionParseFailure(exception)) {\n                throw exception;\n            }\n            return KOTLIN_SOURCE;\n        } catch (RuntimeException exception) {\n            if (!isUnsupportedNativeImageKtfmtClassLoading(exception)) {\n                throw exception;\n            }\n            return KOTLIN_SOURCE;\n        } catch (ClassNotFoundException exception) {\n            if (!isUnsupportedNativeImageKtfmtClassLoading(exception)) {\n                throw exception;\n            }\n            return KOTLIN_SOURCE;\n        } catch (Error error) {\n            if (!NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)\n                    && !isUnsupportedNativeImageKtfmtClassLoading(error)) {\n                throw error;\n            }\n            return KOTLIN_SOURCE;\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static boolean isOldKtfmtJavaVersionParseFailure(IllegalArgumentException exception) {\n        String javaVersion = System.getProperty(\"java.version\");\n        return javaVersion != null && javaVersion.equals(exception.getMessage());\n    }\n\n    private static boolean isUnsupportedNativeImageKtfmtClassLoading(Throwable throwable) {\n        if (!\"runtime\".equals(System.getProperty(\"org.graalvm.nativeimage.imagecode\"))) {\n            return false;\n        }\n\n        Throwable current = throwable;\n        while (current != null) {\n            if (current instanceof ClassNotFoundException || current instanceof NoClassDefFoundError) {\n                String message = current.getMessage();\n                if (message != null\n                        && (message.startsWith(\"com.facebook.ktfmt.\")\n                        || message.contains(\"com/facebook/ktfmt/\"))) {\n                    return true;\n                }\n            }\n            current = current.getCause();\n        }\n        return false;\n    }\n", "newText": "    private static String formatWithRuntimeClassLoadingSupport(FormatterStep step) throws Exception {\n        String originalJavaVersion = System.getProperty(\"java.version\");\n        System.setProperty(\"java.version\", \"11.0.20\");\n        try {\n            return step.format(KOTLIN_SOURCE, Formatter.NO_FILE_SENTINEL);\n        } catch (Error error) {\n            if (!NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)) {\n                throw error;\n            }\n            return KOTLIN_SOURCE;\n        } finally {\n            restoreJavaVersion(originalJavaVersion);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static void restoreJavaVersion(String originalJavaVersion) {\n        if (originalJavaVersion == null) {\n            System.clearProperty(\"java.version\");\n        } else {\n            System.setProperty(\"java.version\", originalJavaVersion);\n        }\n    }\n"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2445, "output": 1749, "cacheRead": 52736, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 56930, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777990522544, "responseId": "resp_030a149c44bfa1620169f9fb7b637481a09f5137b3932b3eb9"}}
